full_summary:
### **Government Tender Announcement: SMP - Electrical Spares**

#### **Notice ID**: W8486-249445/A
#### **Tender Status**: Expired

**Important Details**

* **Solicitation Number**: W8486-249445/A
* **Publication Date**: December 7, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date**: February 29, 2024, at 14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: March 29, 2024
* **Expected Contract End Date**: July 31, 2024

**Tender Description**

The Department of National Defence is seeking bids for the procurement of electrical spares as per the attached documents. The solicitation is under the Request for Proposal (RFP) method, with a competitive process open to all interested bidders.

**Items Required**

Below is a list of required items:

| Item # | Description | Quantity | Unit of Issue |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1    | ABN Number    |          |       |
|     | valve.parts  |          |       |
| 2    | derailleur    |          |       |
|     | gearing.parts |          |       |
| 3    | Electric curb |          |       |
|     | Controls       |          |       |
| 4    | Base plate    |          |       |
|     | electronics    |          |       |

... and so on.

**Submission Requirements**

* A bidder must include their name and contact information on all documents submitted.
* Annex C – Non-Disclosure agreement must be signed by bidders.
* List of plans and drawings (LPD) is available upon request to the Contracting Authority.
* Bidders must provide evidence of Goods and Service Tax (GST) in the bid submission.

**Contact Information**

The point of contact for this tender is Erin Carter, at erin.carter@forces.gc.ca. Questions regarding the tender should be directed to this email address.

**Submission**

Bids must be submitted electronically, via email to DLP53BidsReceiving.DAAT53Receptiondessoumissions@forces.gc.ca. The deadline for bid submission is February 29, 2024, at 14:00:00. Any bid received after this time will not be accepted.

**Trade Agreements**

Please refer to the document for details on any trade agreements that may apply to this procurement.
